snippet.title: Kardboard Kings: Card Game Island | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Kardboard Kings Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1298480/Kardboard_Kings/

Card Game Island comes out on PC and Nintendo Switch on December 8th!

Open your own Card shop by the seaside! Buy, trade and sell Cards, OR keep them for your own collection! Earn reputation with customers, beat your shop goals, unlock new decorations, and host exciting events to bring everyone to the best Card shop in town!

To learn more about Henry's House, Akupara Games, and Kardboard Kings visit:
►Henry's House: https://www.henryshouse.com.au/
►Akupara Games: linktr.ee/akuparagames
►Kardboard Kings: https://linktr.ee/kardboardkings
